# DYSA Ecosystem Engine v3.0

## Auto-Use Policy

ALL skills, plugins, MCPs, agents, and tools MUST be used PROACTIVELY and AUTOMATICALLY without waiting for manual invocation. Claude detects context and uses the right tool immediately.

## Project Intelligence Engine

At the START of every new session:
1. Check if `.claude/PROJECT_PROFILE.json` exists
2. If NO → Run the full detection pipeline:
   ```bash
   python3 .claude/skills/project-intelligence/scripts/detect_project.py "$(pwd)"
   python3 .claude/skills/project-intelligence/scripts/orchestrate.py "$(pwd)" --summary
   ```
3. If YES → Load profile, verify health, report status

